languages.text: "Кто такой этот К'тан? И что он тут делает?"
"What is this C'tan Shard? And what is it doing here?"
languages.original_text: "Кто такой этот К'тан? И что он тут делает?"

traits.locale_text: "Who is this C'Tan? And what is he doing here?"
"Who is this C'Tan? And what is he doing here?"
"Who is this the C'Tan? And what is he doing here?"
"Who is this the C'Tan? And what is he doing here?"
"What is this C'tan? And what is it doing here?"
"What is this C'tan Shard? And what is it doing here?"

languages.text: « Qu'est-ce au juste que le C'tan ? Et que fait-il ici ? »
languages.original_text: "What is this C'tan Shard? And what is it doing here?"

traits.locale_text: « Qui est le C'tan ? Et que fait-il ici ? »

languages.text: «¿Qué es este Fragmento de C'tan? ¿Y qué hace aquí?».
languages.original_text: "What is this C'tan Shard? And what is it doing here?"

traits.locale_text: «¿Qué es el C'Tan? ¿Y qué hace aquí?».

languages.text: “这个‘星神碎片’究竟是什么东西？它在这里做什么？”
languages.original_text: "What is this C'tan Shard? And what is it doing here?"

traits.locale_text: “这个‘星神’究竟是什么东西？它在这里做什么？”

languages.text: "Was ist das dieses C'tan-Fragment? Und was tut es hier?"
languages.original_text: "What is this C'tan Shard? And what is it doing here?"

traits.locale_text: "Wer ist dieser C'tan? Und was tut er hier?"

languages.text: 「ク＝タン・シャードとは？そして、なぜここに？」
languages.original_text: "What is this C'tan Shard? And what is it doing here?"

traits.locale_text: 「ク＝タンとは何者だ？ここで何をしている？」
